{"word":"συνερέω","slug":"συνερέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνερέω</b></el> <el>(attic <el>-ερῶ</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>no <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> in use\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>for <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a>, <a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <a href='S:συναγορεύω'><el>συναγορεύω</el></a>\n<el>(<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-είρηκα</el>) </el><p/><i>to speak with</i> or <i>together, advocate, support in a speech</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}